&lt;li&gt;Track and report on program performance, providing data-driven insights to improve future initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance execution excellence with strategic thinking—identifying new opportunities to drive pipeline and deepen engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
